  "remarks": "Considered a fugitive from justice by the Italian authorities and sentenced in absentia to 6 years detention on 20 Nov. 2008. Sentenced in Tunisia to 4 years imprisonment for terrorist activity and in detention in Tunisia as at Jun. 2009. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020.; Listing: Listed by the UN 1267 Committee on 2 August 2006 (amended on 1 Sep. 2009, 25 Jan. 2010, 13 Dec. 2011, 24 Nov. 2020)",
